title: Review: Conjuring The Devil Made Me Do it
note:
Characters are portrayed stunningly. 
Ruairi O'Connor made a powerful performance. 
Both Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson are as always, very effective in the roles of Lorraine and Ed Warren. 
The tension building up in the climax was supported by the strong performance of the antagonist.
